1. *Zvezde* su se pojavile između oblaka. (The stars appeared between the clouds.)
2. *Zvezda* je bila tako sjajna. (The star was so bright.)
3. On se zaljubio u *zvezdu*. (He fell in love with the star.)
4. Ona gleda u *zvezde*. (She is looking at the stars.)
5. *Zvezdama* se divio. (He admired the stars.)
6. On se zvanično proslavio kada je postao *zvezda*. (He officially became famous when he became a star.)